text: Ra juna manisaharule aphula'i isa'i bhandachan hamile tiniharubata pani vaca li'eka thiyaum tara tiniharule pani tyasako thulo bhaga birsihale, ani hamile pani tiniharuko bicama kiyamatako dinasam'ma satruta ra ghrna jagrta gara'ihalyau ra sighra nai allahale tiniharula'i tinako karmako janakari dinecha
